<!-- How to run the project -->
Since no framework was required to use.I mad used of html,css and a simple javascript code.
create a new folder   (name it any name of your choice)
open Vscode
create three files under the root folder
index.html
style.css
app.js
write a piece of code of what was asked inside and save all.
Click on the live server and it will navigate you to your browser to view or see the output.

